--
-- Structure: 18 standards across 3 safeguard categories (Administrative,
-- Physical, Technical) plus Organizational requirements and Documentation.
-- Each standard has Required (R) or Addressable (A) implementation specs.
--
-- Target modules: dpms (PHI privacy), isms (security), tprm (BAAs)
-- ============================================================================

